{"tid":1808341,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"(先聯署第一步)要求香港真雙普選作為第二階段中美貿易協議一部份","createTime":"2020-01-02T10:02:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T17:09:31.000Z","uid":76310,"like":61,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"57766a05e0e93fb8b2e8c990e5669b83c3097d94","tid":1808341,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:02:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/appeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fappeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPtagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=bdb6249c\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/appeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china</a><br />\n要求香港真雙普選作為第二階段中美貿易協議一部份<br />\n簽左先<br />\n同時, 我地要搵gphone, 周庭, 遊說團體等去遊說呢樣野<br />\n仲有我地要twitter, fb, reddit向各政界人仕, 向各商界人仕推銷呢樣野<br />\n如果說服足夠多既人, 就有機會將香港真雙普選加入為第二階段中美貿易協議一部份<br />\n到時強国唔簽協議, 就一齊攬炒啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外羅所門吹雞<br />\nSolomon Yue<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SolomonYue/status/1210839607526350848?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue%2Fstatus%2F1210839607526350848%3Fs%3D20&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPtagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=5fd8db02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue%2Fstatus%2F1210839607526350848%3Fs%3D20&h=0cd12802\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SolomonYue/status/1210839607526350848?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\nPetition:<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/beijing-2022-winter-olympics-corporate-sponsors-dont-deserve-tax-benefits-so-dont-help-them-fund-ccp-propaganda-again\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fbeijing-2022-winter-olympics-corporate-sponsors-dont-deserve-tax-benefits-so-dont-help-them-fund-ccp-propaganda-again&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPtagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=6cb717a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/beijing-2022-winter-olympics-corporate-sponsors-dont-deserve-tax-benefits-so-dont-help-them-fund-ccp-propaganda-again</a>"},{"pid":"4186362e10adac51d02bedc8268905c330c780b8","tid":1808341,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:02:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"715fe05401d1ee3925e9ab741ccdc18bb42e00c0","tid":1808341,"uid":76310,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:03:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LpbTZPn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLpbTZPn.jpg&h=910d17cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"71170c5715f251f37158fb3eaf829f0ab3f2dcee","tid":1808341,"uid":153186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:04:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e988bb60ce1dce71792165254acf9140a9e304ae","tid":1808341,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:08:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />1<br />\n直接打大佬都唔簽？"},{"pid":"c87a3ad3da303198ed6442b27969e31b02fbd181","tid":1808341,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:11:40.000Z",